## Deploy Super Rialo HQ to GitHub Pages

### First Time Setup:

```bash
# 1. Create repo on GitHub (https://github.com/new)
# Name: super-rialo-hq, Public, Don't initialize

# 2. Push code to GitHub (replace YOUR_USERNAME)
cd /app
git init
git add .
git commit -m \"Initial commit\"
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/super-rialo-hq.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main

# 3. Deploy to GitHub Pages
cd frontend
yarn deploy

# 4. Enable GitHub Pages in repo settings:
# Settings > Pages > Source: gh-pages branch > Save
```

### Your Game Will Be Live At:
```
https://YOUR_USERNAME.github.io/super-rialo-hq/
```

### Update Game Later:
```bash
cd /app/frontend
yarn deploy
```

That's it! ðŸŽ®
